{"tid":1174675,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【童年崩壞】的士陳缺氧式唱中文版A Whole New World","createTime":"2019-05-28T04:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T05:24:56.000Z","uid":89543,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7c43413ea592972a80baf50ba6b77fe165b4c4","tid":1174675,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2835009/org/2777a3064f21557ee3819655bc6cb308.jpg/NqbSjRyWf1z1B1pQ0q3J0i7nU6KdHEF1SxCYUUsQmFE?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2835009%2Forg%2F2777a3064f21557ee3819655bc6cb308.jpg%2FNqbSjRyWf1z1B1pQ0q3J0i7nU6KdHEF1SxCYUUsQmFE%3Fv%3Dw640&h=d98b0d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日迪士尼真人電影《阿拉丁》正式上映，不少迪士尼粉絲紛紛到電影院朝聖，為的當然是在「Dolby Atmos」的震撼下欣賞全新版本的《A Whole new World》。作為阿拉丁的主題曲，《A Whole New World》已是迪士尼其中一首最具代表性的合唱情歌。就連電影兩位男女主角，Mena Massoud及Naomi Scott也經迪士尼精挑細選的唱得之人，故此電影上映後，二人的合唱版已備受讚譽。<br />\n不過近日釋出了《A Whole New World》的中文版主題曲《新的世界》，反差可說令人咋舌，因為兩位主唱分別是由陳偉霆及張碧晨擔當。其實張碧晨擔任女主音也相當適合，始終她是《中國好聲音》第三季的總冠軍，無疑是唱得之人，聲線亦跟歌曲原唱非常相近。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">但問題便出在男主唱陳偉霆身上，一向William的舞技及演技也是眾所周知的「突出」。不過偏偏唱功便完全被埋沒忽略，今次翻唱《A Whole New World》簡直是揚名立萬的第一步，其斷氣缺氧式唱法，令不少網民聽後也懷疑人生，有人問：「陳偉霆到底是怎麼紅的？」，更有網民表示終於感受到「來回地獄又折返人間」的真諦。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9f8QLjnFkqc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9f8QLjnFkqc&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQX0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=e0b6efc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9f8QLjnFkqc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6e1d80cb7c18affa1c2ce2746ff6fd480506b5","tid":1174675,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044adc00184676121aa9e1302300a8333586f639","tid":1174675,"uid":129592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:02:59.000Z","msg":"點解男女聲可以咁唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5840a0f6eab87cced31a463048e249fb17c670d0","tid":1174675,"uid":159454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"的士陳把聲完全唔入咪<br />\n好似啲人用屋企咪加cover 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02034575f8d6bdeca9ee552d2778a4e658ccc548","tid":1174675,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:36:37.000Z","msg":"路遙知馬力"},{"pid":"6592bb8f74abec4c27ffa317a70e69613e59c8c5","tid":1174675,"uid":251836,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MDwhqwC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDwhqwC.gif&h=2785d3b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"441e46776975bde1ca93aee858b6f3f823901f8c","tid":1174675,"uid":93112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wayZz8aFV3M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwayZz8aFV3M&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQX0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=4d4b8743\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wayZz8aFV3M</a>"},{"pid":"9de46b7528dcc26850dd6c4c19f8c63a89be6d10","tid":1174675,"uid":251197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:24:56.000Z","msg":"難聽"}]}